      "title": "[正面] It can be a bit too tough, especially in the begin...",
      "summary": "It can be a bit too tough, especially in the beginning. But after lvl 20-25 it should be easier. Though, still hard to master. This game is a gacha but it is unique and different than most of the others out there. It has a steep learning curve and it requires for you to exercise your brain on how to do some things. Aside that, it can be fairly good experience. So far as a new player I am really enjoying this. I hope I can keep enjoying this game.",
